@APITask_HostAddress = https://localhost:7110
@TaskId = 8

### Listar todas as tarefas
GET {{APITask_HostAddress}}/api/tasks
Accept: application/json

### Filtrar por status
GET {{APITask_HostAddress}}/api/tasks?status=Pending
Accept: application/json

### Filtrar por prioridade
GET {{APITask_HostAddress}}/api/tasks?priority=High
Accept: application/json

### Buscar tarefa por ID
GET {{APITask_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/{{TaskId}}
Accept: application/json

### Criar tarefa
POST {{APITask_HostAddress}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Revisar documentação",
  "description": "Atualizar exemplos do arquivo .http",
  "priority": 2
}

### Atualizar tarefa parcialmente
PATCH {{APITask_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/{{TaskId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 1,
  "priority": 2
}

### Deletar tarefa
DELETE {{APITask_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/{{TaskId}}
Accept: application/json
